<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-4F98FF8D-283F-4A20-A60B-798BC2038939" version="2" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-4F98FF8D-283F-4A20-A60B-798BC2038939" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Extended installation wizard steps (part 1) ( R4.3 and higher)</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="M148553-B105"><p class="- topic/p ">The first part contains the configuration settings of the engine and end with a reboot to activate the settings made. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="SECTION_F0C46BBCD2F642BC89CFC563F50CE61E" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Part 1: until the first reboot</title><table id="TABLE_AB12398ADAC24FBF9EA1C29CD821223F" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" align="left" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" align="left" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="90*" align="left" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the language you want to execute the wizard in. 
</p><fig id="GUID-3DA36A72-96A7-4B81-8A75-032ABECADC18" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C00EB79C-CE2F-46F0-BE62-F1A1E8A5258C-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C00EB79C-CE2F-46F0-BE62-F1A1E8A5258C-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Press<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Next</b> to accept the End User License Agreement (EULA). Decline is not possible. 
</p><fig id="GUID-22B7BA54-E530-4DEC-8401-1E8DC7F0C736" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6F34C816-AFC8-417F-AC8C-3F36C6781BB7-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6F34C816-AFC8-417F-AC8C-3F36C6781BB7-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Set the time zone to the time zone where the machine is placed in. 
</p><fig id="GUID-A381EB65-8868-4F3F-99B6-0FFF4BC46FE6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1355E1EC-744A-4796-B71A-08413B1AD3B9-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1355E1EC-744A-4796-B71A-08413B1AD3B9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Set the date and time correctly to make sure that the accounting information or customer is set correctly, just as the machine logging for service. 
</p><fig id="GUID-D610D9E5-F899-4DB8-BD79-E7377180AA46" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-AC7EEADB-4820-4BD6-B5D7-DDF640C69EC4-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-AC7EEADB-4820-4BD6-B5D7-DDF640C69EC4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Please keep this setting to 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">“Always”</b>. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Other keys with alternative software will not be installed. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The system is protected to only use Colorado Series installation packages. 
</p><fig id="GUID-EBD1AEF2-9884-4859-BEA4-F4EFE901381B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-75F22C26-D0E4-4EA1-8592-F7DFD6C7606A-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-75F22C26-D0E4-4EA1-8592-F7DFD6C7606A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Fill the hostname as requested by the customer. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> In the site survey a hostname should be indicated. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Otherwise leave the hostname as proposed by the system. 
</p><fig id="GUID-81FA50AC-D412-404A-992B-BA83E825FA42" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-30D8BEA9-5F9D-4857-AF6D-4AEA5828C3D8-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-30D8BEA9-5F9D-4857-AF6D-4AEA5828C3D8-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Unless specifically mentioned in the site survey leave the setting to automatic. 
</p><fig id="GUID-DB44C242-4099-4699-A90B-8828570A760A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4DC2145C-4E96-4B0A-90B5-610F22F2C730-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4DC2145C-4E96-4B0A-90B5-610F22F2C730-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Unless specifically mentioned in the site survey leave the settings as is. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">TCP/IP, DHCP, IPv4, IPv6, subnet, gateway, DNS 
</p><fig id="GUID-23A09115-5BB1-4874-A838-F28BBB45B95C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E5945CD6-1BC9-48ED-9CBE-B26F383F55B5-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E5945CD6-1BC9-48ED-9CBE-B26F383F55B5-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Unless specifically mentioned in the site survey leave the proxy server settings as is. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Proxy server, port, authentication 
</p><fig id="GUID-483A24D1-3ADF-4213-B92F-35BC7E9B8E83" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A06FF7E0-E9A8-4D3B-BCE4-9BAA37A9E90D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A06FF7E0-E9A8-4D3B-BCE4-9BAA37A9E90D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> When actions towards the Embedded Controller are initiated a SAM key needs to be inserted. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When a SAM key is already inserted it may look like this step is skipped. 
</p><fig id="GUID-20B758A6-CAC7-412C-9CAF-C2E0BDF51C06" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4F06EE4B-F9BA-4321-90F8-837248AA512D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4F06EE4B-F9BA-4321-90F8-837248AA512D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Part of alternative scenario</b> : 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> No valid SAM key is detected. 
</p><fig id="GUID-2608CA08-C792-4051-8C7C-2FFD807F591F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C30A3887-1E07-40EB-9582-A2B8E405A924-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C30A3887-1E07-40EB-9582-A2B8E405A924-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">A key is detected but an error is detected. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The reason is reported in the highlighted section of the screenshot. 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Invalid license 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Key is expired 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Key certification is too old. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Access is denied 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">"Host not found” 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">User(SERVICE) is disabled 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Reason unknown. 
</p></li></ul><fig id="GUID-AC24AAEE-485A-4F62-A027-D89C5CC97333" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DC93195B-4BDE-41E7-A8D8-C9164973567F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DC93195B-4BDE-41E7-A8D8-C9164973567F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Confirm the installation status of the optional printhead designated for white printing. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If the printhead for white printing is currently installed, set the value to 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Yes</b>. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If the white printing option will be installed later, set the value to 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">No</b>. 
</p><note id="GUID-1300A9C7-8D2F-49B8-8039-5B07BFEDA100" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">when "initializing..." is displayed, there might be a delay before the popup appears. 
</p></note><fig id="GUID-536DFBC8-F465-4F8D-B539-5EBB80B8D1EF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-269C3EBC-45AD-442C-B88D-7CF2CA26C6C0-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-269C3EBC-45AD-442C-B88D-7CF2CA26C6C0-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">14 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Indicate the type of filtering that will be used with this machine. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Specify the filtration method to be employed for this machine: internal filtering or an external filtering unit. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If the printer will be equipped with an external filtering unit at a later stage, select 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"internal" 
</b>for now and ensure the internal filters are properly positioned. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Incorrect filter setup can lead to safety concerns. 
</p><fig id="GUID-F8DE7DF8-89D1-48DB-B7D2-C671FB08B4CE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-8EB8BA80-4FB6-4DF5-9714-5C1C8B1CCF7B-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-8EB8BA80-4FB6-4DF5-9714-5C1C8B1CCF7B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">15 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> All the settings that need to be incorporated are set now. Press 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Next</b> to restart and apply the settings. 
</p><fig id="GUID-8A6FFE3B-2591-4EFD-82CC-ED9032B039DE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4314D3D9-77CB-4B9A-A118-91ADC5092716-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4314D3D9-77CB-4B9A-A118-91ADC5092716-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row valign="top" class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">16 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-C84BCEB1-6CB4-4219-9A2F-C7890FAD6C04" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-29CD8FFD-ABBA-45C8-8F54-28501F7B1E89-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-29CD8FFD-ABBA-45C8-8F54-28501F7B1E89-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-7D3F358C-1AB9-4A5D-9B0E-C75D689F152E.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
